Grace Hartman (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grace_Hartman_(actress) 0 Grace Hartman (January 7, 1907 – August 8, 1955) was an American stage and musical theatre actress. She was born San Francisco, California. She was married to actor Paul Hartman from 1927 until the time of her death, Van Nuys, California, in 1955.
